text:
Recently, a gay pride celebration for DeGeneres exploded into a furious bust-up between the talk queen and her wife, as RadarOnline.com readers know. The embattled couple was at a private party toasting Ellen's 20-year anniversary. "Portia kept trying to talk to Ellen, but Ellen wouldn't even look at her as she screeched out of the parking lot!" said a source.
